{"tid":85508,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗主家中虐打狗隻  自稱是司警  聲言「條片流出街就告你」","createTime":"2017-01-18T11:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T16:17:33.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5167df96a7f5de8e7aec64daf6d9242c4d96249","tid":85508,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:20:56.000Z","msg":"【愛瞞報道】（去片）狗主家中虐打狗隻  自稱是司警  聲言「條片流出街就告你」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歡迎光臨中國澳門</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（最新消息：司警局證實虐狗狗主為刑偵人員，又指狗隻受虐情況，未足以構成刑事成分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。詳情請看 <a href=\"https://goo.gl/qe9w7J\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fqe9w7J&d=erJmOM8fZSHGPbp4jMaRNhpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=174164f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/qe9w7J</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n（澳門電台：狗主承認曾拍打狗隻，但就拒絕跟隨治安警返警局協助調查。）<br />\n<br />\n有讀者報料稱，昨日下午有居民目睹，位於氹仔孫逸仙博士大馬路利民大廈一個單位平台，一名男子抱起一狗隻再摔地上，再用物件多次擊打和腳踢。而網上流傳相關虐打片段，可見虐打長約30多秒，期間可聽到有鄰居大叫「唔好再打，停手」。<br />\n<br />\n據消息指，有人已即時致電民政總署和治安警報案，亦有動物協會的人員到場了解。而虐打狗隻的男子是該狗狗主，疑因為狗隻咬爛主人的鞋子所以被施虐。但該狗主向到場了解的人士聲稱，他是一名司警，更聲言若有關虐打片段「流出街」，就會「告」拍下短片的人士。<br />\n<br />\n目前未知狗隻的受傷情況，至於案件的處理，以及狗主是否是司警，《愛瞞》已向治安警查詢，惟至截稿前仍未收到回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/macauconcealers/videos/1206343702768062/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmacauconcealers%2Fvideos%2F1206343702768062%2F&d=erJmOM8fZSHGPbp4jMaRNhpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=c6ba174f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/macauconcealers/videos/1206343702768062/</a>"},{"pid":"eb07fdffb80cd510f92448e2056f70ed140aa4f7","tid":85508,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:19:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b38309a47f9ea0fd326b35dca405b36c7d9833f","tid":85508,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:41:47.000Z","msg":"澳門 狗也不屌之地"},{"pid":"6468de84abedf273f4d546d065fc751a57dfb771","tid":85508,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:17:33.000Z","msg":"天下警犬一樣<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[black]黑[/black]</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}